---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { t, type Lang } from '../../i18n/ui';

interface Props { lang: Lang }
const { lang } = Astro.props;
const isEn = lang === 'en';
---

<Base
  title={isEn ? 'Snow at Huxin Pavilion' : '湖心亭看雪'}
  description={isEn
    ? 'Zhang Dai\'s "all in white", made into a lake you can row into.'
    : '把张岱的「上下一白」做成可以划进去的湖。'}
  lang={lang}
>
  <article class="story">
    <header class="story-hero" data-fade>
      <p class="story-eyebrow">Interactive · 2026</p>
      <h1 class="story-title">{isEn ? 'Snow at Huxin Pavilion' : '湖心亭看雪'}</h1>
      <p class="story-sub">{isEn
        ? 'Zhang Dai\'s "all in white", made into a lake you can row into.'
        : '把「上下一白」做成可以划进去的湖。'}</p>
    </header>

    <div class="story-body">
      <figure class="story-figure">
        <a href="/snow/" aria-label={isEn ? 'Enter the interactive scene of Snow at Huxin Pavilion' : '进入湖心亭看雪互动场景'}>
          <img
            src="/projects/snow/card.jpg"
            alt={isEn ? 'West Lake on a snowy night: a small boat heading for Huxin Pavilion' : '雪夜西湖：小舟驶向湖心亭'}
            loading="eager"
          />
        </a>
      </figure>

      {isEn ? (
        <>
          <p>
            The best part of Zhang Dai's snow writing is in the measure words: the long embankment a trace, Huxin Pavilion a dot, my boat a speck, and the people in it two or three grains. I used AI to build a three-dimensional West Lake on a snowy night, and made each of those tiny "ones" a scene you can row into.
          </p>
          <p>
            Click the water and the boat rows there by itself; or hold "Row" or the space bar to paddle slowly. After three days of heavy snow, all sounds of people and birds have left the lake — you head for the pavilion alone. Once there, why not step ashore and sit a while: the people in the pavilion are already warming wine by the stove.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a class="story-link" href="/snow/">Row alone to Huxin Pavilion →</a>
          </p>
        </>
      ) : (
        <>
          <p>
            张岱写雪，最妙是那几个量词：长堤一痕、湖心亭一点、与余舟一芥、舟中人两三粒。我用 AI 生成了一座三维的雪夜西湖，把这几个「一」做成可以划进去的场景。
          </p>
          <p>
            点击水面，船会自己划过去；也可以按住「划桨」或空格慢慢摇。大雪三日，湖中人鸟声俱绝，你一个人往湖心亭去。到了亭前，不妨登亭一坐——亭中人已在炉边温酒。
          </p>
          <p>
            <a class="story-link" href="/snow/">独往湖心亭 →</a>
          </p>
        </>
      )}
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .story {
    padding: 0 96px 160px;
  }

  .story-hero {
    max-width: 768px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 160px 0 72px;
  }

  .story-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 22px;
    letter-spacing: -0.28px;
    color: #707070;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .story-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 60px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 72px;
    letter-spacing: -1.2px;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 60px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 72px;
    letter-spacing: -1.2px;
    color: #707070;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-body {
    max-width: 768px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 42px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-body p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }

  .story-figure {
    margin: 48px 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .story-figure:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .story-figure img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    transition: opacity 200ms;
  }

  .story-figure a:hover img {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .story-link {
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 6px;
    transition: color 200ms;
  }

  .story-link:hover {
    color: #707070;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story {
      padding: 0 24px 80px;
    }

    .story-hero {
      padding: 120px 0 56px;
    }

    .story-title,
    .story-sub {
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 44px;
      letter-spacing: -0.72px;
    }

    .story-body p {
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 33px;
    }

    .story-figure {
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
